summary: Expanded onto the Alchemist\'s Shack in the Rift.
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple house that I built next the Alchemist\'s Shack in the Rift. Currrently, the interior of the new shack is mostly a copy of Froki\'s Shack, but with the NPC\'s gone along with their ownship. The basement has a crafting equipment. Eventually I plan on making the buildings live up to their name more.

I\'m open to suggestions as to what I should change.
author: Brdn666
